<title>BELGIUM: Belgium to impose tax on bearer certificates.</title>
<headline>Belgium to impose tax on bearer certificates.</headline>
<dateline>BRUSSELS 1996-10-01</dateline>
<text>
<p>The Belgian government said on Tuesday it would impose a tax of 0.002 percent on the deposit of bearer certificates, which would give it a positive budget impact of four billion francs.</p>
<p>The government said in a statement the measure was aimed at boosting transactions in dematerialised certificates.</p>
